message: "If you use SingleRepExplorer, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "SingleRepExplorer: An Interactive Web Application for Integrated Single-Cell Transcriptomic and Immune Repertoire Analysis"
version: "1.0.0"
date-released: "2026-04-27"
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/amufaamo/SingleRepExplorer"
