abstract: >-
  SingleRepExplorer is a web-based interactive tool that integrates single-cell
  RNA-seq transcriptomic analysis with TCR/BCR immune repertoire profiling in a
  single no-code platform. Built on R Shiny and distributed via Docker, it
  enables biologists without programming expertise to perform clustering,
  differential expression, pathway enrichment, trajectory inference, cell-cell
  communication, and clonotype analyses through an intuitive GUI.
